  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to compare patients' satisfaction from the use of three different
      inhalation devices by using the FSI-10 questionnaire
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients are requested to reply to FSI-10 questionnaire regarding their satisfaction from
      inhalation devices. Patients are on 3 different asthma inhalation devices with combination
      treatment (Turbuhaler, Diskus, Elpenhaler)
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
